query:
WITH inserted AS (
            INSERT INTO event_game_schedule (
                event_id,
                game_id,
                start_time,
                duration_minutes,
                is_pinned
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
            RETURNING
                id,
                event_id,
                game_id,
                start_time,
                duration_minutes,
                is_pinned,
                created_at,
                last_modified
        )
        SELECT
            inserted.id,
            inserted.event_id,
            inserted.game_id,
            sg.name AS game_name,
            inserted.start_time,
            inserted.duration_minutes,
            inserted.is_pinned,
            inserted.created_at,
            inserted.last_modified
        FROM inserted
        INNER JOIN steam_game sg ON inserted.game_id = sg.appid
